sect2.para:
Get the latest Checkclipse kit from SourceForge at
and install it by unzipping into your Eclipse plugins directory and restarting Eclipse. (Checkstyle is bundled with Checkclipse so it's not necessary to install it separately, but the web site is
for reference.)
